In the service industry, an enterprise resource planning (ERP) system is a vital 
tool as many moving parts, must work in sync every day to ensure that the 
organization operates at its optimum level.
Listed below are five ways ERP streamlines hotel and resort operations:
•Room booking system;
•Guest management;
•Front -desk efficiency;
•Inventory management; and
•Housekeeping, laundry, and maintenance.
